=========================
HTTP/1.1 201 Created
Content-Length: 109
Content-Type: application/json
Date: REGEX(.*)

[
    "urn:ngsi-ld:TemperatureSensor:002",
    "urn:ngsi-ld:TemperatureSensor:003",
    "urn:ngsi-ld:TemperatureSensor:004"
]


02. Update two of them using Batch Update, one with a correct entity type present and the other one without entity type
=======================================================================================================================
HTTP/1.1 204 No Content
Date: REGEX(.*)



03. Get the entities to see the modifications
=============================================
HTTP/1.1 200 OK
Content-Length: 543
Content-Type: application/json
Link: <https://uri.etsi.org/ngsi-ld/v1/ngsi-ld-core-context.jsonld>; rel="http://www.w3.org/ns/json-ld#context"; type="application/ld+json"
Date: REGEX(.*)

[
    {
        "category": {
            "type": "Property",
            "value": "sensor"
        },
        "id": "urn:ngsi-ld:TemperatureSensor:002",
        "temperature": {
            "type": "Property",
            "unitCode": "CEL",
            "value": 20
        },
        "type": "TemperatureSensor"
    },
    {
        "category": {
            "type": "Property",
            "value": "sensor2"
        },
        "id": "urn:ngsi-ld:TemperatureSensor:003",
        "temperature": {
            "type": "Property",
            "unitCode": "CEL",
            "value": 2
        },
        "type": "TemperatureSensor"
    },
    {
        "category": {
            "type": "Property",
            "value": "sensor3"
        },
        "id": "urn:ngsi-ld:TemperatureSensor:004",
        "temperature": {
            "type": "Property",
            "unitCode": "CEL",
            "value": 101
        },
        "type": "TemperatureSensor"
    }
]


--TEARDOWN--
brokerStop CB
dbDrop CB
